To produce binary:
  cd ./src
  make

Some important configuration files
Work's thread TCL script                     - ./src/tcl/wrkThread.tcl
Configuration and administration TCL script - ./src/tcl/admin.tcl

to start Demo - switch in src directory - cd ./src
There are different mods to run demo:
  ./its
    - run as command line program with log to <stdout> (gut for debugger)
  ./its -D -d 4 -f /tmp/its_demo.log
    run as a daemon - production mode
	-D   - switch in daemon mode
        -d # - log level (4 is max one)
        -f <...> - log-file
